Pages Module
============

Models
------

Node : SortableMTNode // PolyModel
 // properties
 - name       -- The name of the folder

 // metadata
 - slug       -- autogenerated
 - breadcrumb -- breadcrumb name
 - updated    -- datetime // automatically updated on each put
 - author     -- the last one who updaed the file (we only need: last updated by) // automatically updated on each put
 - status     -- (Hidden, Draft, Published)
 - active     -- True/False weather or not that page is considered

Folder : Node 
  pass

Page : Node
 // metadata
 - description-- description for the html metadata
 - keywords   -- list of comma seperated keywords for inclusion in the html metadata

 // content
 - body       -- page body, will be first processed using jinja, so {% %} tags are availabe for plugins and then truough markdown
                 - need a |jinja filter that pushes the content though jinja.
 - html       -- the cached page result

Views
-----

- Add Folder
- Add Page
- Edit Folder
- Edit Page
- Manage (to switch between active/passive folder, use ipod style on/off switch)
- Delete

